\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gyq1665702827435.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gyq1665702827435.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gyq1665702827435.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gyq1665702827435\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Drag and Drop Properties\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define the Drag and Drop properties of a picture widget or of an item in a tree widget.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__p_d8912e1_d8913e1_d8914e1\">You can select a format in the list of library formats and copy it to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Supported Drag Formats</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Allowed Drop Formats</span> lists using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">&lt;</span> button.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__p_d8915e1_d8916e1_d8917e1\">Add a format by typing using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">+</span> button.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__p_d8918e1_d8919e1_d8920e1\">Remove a format with the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">-</span> button.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__section_nxc_41k_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d659982e75\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__ul_inn_41k_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__li_d4082e1_d4083e1_d4084e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ule1665702637317.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ule1665702637317.html\" title=\"Specifies the drag-and-drop formats that can be used when dragging objects in this widget.\">Supported Drag Formats (DragFormat)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__li_d4085e1_d4086e1_d4087e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"veb1665702637387.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/veb1665702637387.html\" title=\"Specifies the drag-and-drop formats that can be used to use when dropping objects in this widget\">Accepted Drop Formats (DropFormat)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__li_d4088e1_d4089e1_d4090e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"trd1665702827576.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/trd1665702827576.html\" title=\"List of drag-and-drop formats available in the selected library.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__li_d4091e1_d4092e1_d4093e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jxj1665702637457.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jxj1665702637457.html\" title=\"Specifies the accepted drop actions for all selected Drag-and-Drop formats, thereby overriding the actions defined in the formats themselves.\">Use Field Actions for All Drop Formats ( DropActions)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__section_hrk_p1k_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d659982e120\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gyq1665702827435__p_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ieb1705583991220.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ieb1705583991220.html\" title=\"Drag and drop properties are supported by picture widgets and items in the tree widget.\">Defining Drag and Drop Behavior for Picture and Tree Widgets</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eav1719500059023.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag and Drop Behavior</a><p>Drag and drop behavior enables the user to select an object and drag it to another location with the mouse. When the mouse button is released, the selected object is copied, moved, or linked to by a shortcut.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swj1719500297780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oqr1705583543910.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Create and Maintain Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats determine the actions and context menus for dragging and dropping objects in Tree and Picture widgets in desktop applications. They are maintained and deployed in a runtime library.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528100\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Drag and Drop Properties Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Drag and Drop Properties Define the Drag and Drop properties of a picture widget or of an item in a tree widget. You can select a format in the list of library formats and copy it to the Supported Drag Formats or Allowed Drop Formats lists using the < button. Add a format by typing using the + button. Remove a format with the - button. Fields Supported Drag Formats (DragFormat) Accepted Drop Formats (DropFormat) Library Use Field Actions for All Drop Formats ( DropActions) How to Defining Drag and Drop Behavior for Picture and Tree Widgets Related Links Drag and Drop Behavior Drag and drop behavior enables the user to select an object and drag it to another location with the mouse. When the mouse button is released, the selected object is copied, moved, or linked to by a shortcut. Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets. Create and Maintain Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats determine the actions and context menus for dragging and dropping objects in Tree and Picture widgets in desktop applications. They are maintained and deployed in a runtime library. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}